/[Aa]ssets/Plugins/WaveVR/
/[Aa]ssets/Plugins/WindowsMR/
/[Aa]ssets/XRSettings.asset
/[Aa]ssets/OculusSettings.asset
/[Aa]ssets/OpenXRSettings.asset

# Ignore auto-generated XR and platform-specific cache files
[Xx]r[Mm]anagement[Mm]etadata/
[Xx]r[Tt]oolkit[Mm]etadata/
[Xx]r[Pp]latform[Mm]etadata/
[Xx]r[Pp]rovider[Mm]etadata/

